<p>during that hellish time [see <a href="http://drzaius.ics.uci.edu/mt3.14/johannab/archives/2005/04/the_life_and_ti.html">previous post</a>], i did manage to present at the in-house conference that was happening at uci.  and now, for all of you who weren't there, you can <a href="http://www.calit2.net/articles/article.php?id=493">experience the magic</a> of my rivetting talk, which was on my "information stuff."</p>
                              
