                        <h3 class="content">blissed out?</h3>
                        <div class="content">
                           <div class="content">
                              <p><img src="http://drzaius.ics.uci.edu/mt3.14/johannab/archives/afteryoga.jpg" width="198" height="201"></p>

<p>today after 2 long months, i finally hit the mat and did some yoga.  damn did that feel good.  i'm not sure why i even stopped, but "too much work" seems completely preposterous.  there is something about putting your forehead to the floor that makes everything alright. </p>

<p>then i went to <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/ungrok/10608657/">cook</a> some dinner with meta and sled.  caprese, eggplant parmesan, wine... bliss.</p>
                              
                              <p class="posted">
